**[Petite Cathedral Pavé Diamond Engagement Ring in Platinum (1/6 ct. tw.) — $2,010](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-cathedral-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-6-ct-tw-item-194341?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
