**Most-Reviewed Round Halo (for buyers who want maximum sparkle and accept the round-look):**
**[Round Split Band Diamond Halo Engagement Ring in 14K White Gold (JA) — $4,400](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/round-split-band-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-314979?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
